description:
Blamed for her baby brother’s unexplained death, Tracyraquel Berns is tormented by guilt and unanswered questions. Determined to uncover the truth, her investigation leads to shocking revelations, hidden dangers, and connections to other mysterious deaths. As she pieces the puzzle together, Tracyraquel must overcome immense personal and legal challenges to seek justice and finally find peace.

Stream the new true crime docuseries on February 4, exclusively on Paramount+.
